name: FYTE
description:
(fyte=fight) 
This tee features a Moroccan styled female laid over a subtle ancient currency pattern that is also printed on the back. The pattern is a very subtle black on black print and is only visible from close up or when light hits it from the right angle.

	All BattalionArmour men’s tees are 100% Fine Jersey cotton, combed for softness and comfort, but strong and durable for long life and heavy wear.

name: MISL
description: (misl=missile) MISL packs some serious fire power for days when its you against the world. It’s an off white tee with a chocolate battle tank and accents over a subtle contraband eagle design that is also printed on the back of the tee in a very subtle creme on creme print. All BattalionArmour men’s tees are 100% Fine Jersey cotton, combed for softness and comfort, but strong and durable for long life and heavy wear.

name: SARG
KUPL creme
description: (KUPL=Couple) This design was inspired by my love for Koi fish. KUPL is printed on the v-neck sleeveless tee in metallic pink with soft pink birds and Koi swimming together in the background. I love how versatile this design is. You can wear it forward, backward, and inside out forward and backward. Each of these tees are also hand cut and sewn leaving unique details like contrast stitching and unfinished seems. No 2 are alike. And you’ll love the way this v-neck sleeveless tee feels when you put it on. Its cut a bit short in length for summer so you can show a little hip if you wear your jeans low. 100% Baby Rib cotton, combed for softness and comfort. Machine Wash cold, Hang dry. One Size Fits Most.

name: ABUV
description: (abuv=above) This design is about rising above the wars that are unnecessary to fight. Choose your battles wisely because love is truly the only thing worth fighting for. ABUV features a metallic gold design with white accents on a fire red shirt. This one is heavy. All BattalionArmour men’s tees are 100% Fine Jersey cotton, combed for softness and comfort, but strong and durable for long life and heavy wear.
